{"name":"List of Sins","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"misc","data":{"description":"<p>A long and accurate document cross-referenced against reality to discover unseen evil-doers. Successfu Presence DR10: A strange light surrounds evil creatures. The list's owner defends with +2 against any being discovered this way.</p>","equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/icons/classitems/listofsins.png","effects":[],"_id":"4UrTfKWiKIkQz0KY"}
{"name":"The Blasphemous Nechrubel Bible","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"misc","data":{"description":"<p>So intensely blasphemous even the Priests themselves can only peruse it once per day. When read, roll a die.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Even result:</span> For the rest of the day PCs heal d4 HP after just five minutes of rest.</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Odd result:</span> The priest is plagued by demon hallucinations. The DM may invent d3 things that only the Priest can see and describe them to the player as if true. This effect ends with sunrise.</p>","equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/icons/classitems/blasphemousbible.png","effects":[],"_id":"6gfDlDmmdZjA8LJS"}
{"name":"Eurekia","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"weapon","data":{"description":"<p>The cursed sword Eurekia. For every swing of Eurekia roll a d6. On a 1 the squire Hamfund is slain and Eurekia vanishes forever.</p>","equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1,"damageDie":"2d6","handed":"2","weaponType":"melee"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/icons/classitems/eurekia.png","effects":[],"_id":"6php84FjzxVsRvlX"}
{"name":"The Shoe of Death's Horse","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"weapon","data":{"description":"<p>It looks normal but since finding it in an obscure crypt you are convinced this shoe came from the horse of Death himself. In your hands it hits with DR10, d4 damage. 1 in 6 chance the shoe smashes the skull, instantly killing small-to-medium sized creatures. The shoe returns to your hand like a boomerang.</p>","equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1,"damageDie":"1d4","handed":"1","weaponType":"ranged"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/icons/classitems/horseshoe.png","effects":[],"_id":"8LWRa3qy04Mw9IAz"}
{"name":"(WRONG JESUS) CRUCIFIX","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"misc","data":{"description":"<p>The crucifix can be used in encounters with the undead as we as lesser trolls and goblins. Check morale (add or subtract the priest's Presence modifier) to see if the creatures bow and kindly remove themselves.</p>","equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/icons/items/misc/crucifix.png","effects":[],"_id":"Gpmr925qK2xabM6W"}
{"name":"Spider-Owl Soup","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"misc","data":{"description":"<p>See in darkness, climb on walls for 30 minutes.</p>","equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/icons/classitems/herbmasterdecoction.png","effects":[],"_id":"HMlqsgwJX8IueYnx"}
{"name":"Stolen Mitre","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"misc","data":{"description":"<p>While wearing this holy hat the priest's vile body fades, becoming hard to hit in combat (Defense DR10). If pulled over the ears outside of battle the priest becomes nearly invisible, testing stealth against DR8.</p>","equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/icons/classitems/mitre.png","effects":[],"_id":"L8KhtpzLSKqDI5y4"}
{"name":"The Snake-Skin Dagger","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"weapon","data":{"description":"<p>The dagger does d4 damage but on a 1 the target dies immediately of deadly poison weeping from the blade.</p>","equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1,"damageDie":"1d4","handed":"1","weaponType":"melee"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/icons/classitems/snakeskindagger.png","effects":[],"_id":"M8iEq8flJ4Vgk932"}
